          <p>
            Your computer holds your photos, documents, bank details, and years of personal data. Handing it over to a stranger requires trust. Yet many people pick a repair shop based solely on whoever comes up first in a Google search, without knowing how to tell the good from the bad.
          </p>

          <p>
