            <li><strong>Trading since 2007</strong> - nearly two decades of experience and local reputation</li>
            <li><strong>Published pricing</strong> - check my <a href="/pricing/" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan);">pricing page</a> before you even call</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
